---
title: Crumbed Eggplant with Spiced Fries & Plant-Based Basil Pesto
description: Yes, you can whip up an eggplant parma at home — it’s not that hard! At least our version isn’t — with hearty eggplant steaks that
are lightly roasted, then baked to get a golden crumb and tomato topping. Served with a pear salad and tasty fries, this shows you can always improve on the classics!

